{
  "id": "czarna-kaczka",
  "name": "Czarna Kaczka (The Black Duck)",
  "description": "Old Town traditional Polish restaurant centered on duck dishes (the namesake — try the Cracovian or Old-Polish-style roast duck), plus a full lineup of pierogi, soups in bread bowls, tartare, and big game/duck mains. Tourist-friendly but well-regarded; multilingual menu (PL/EN/DE/ES/FR/IT/UA/EL).",
